{
  "stem": "25598.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the soldier told him that these were people who had been taken out from mental hospitals from [NON-ENGLISH]-- Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were not given their clothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were told that they can take the sheets from the hospital beds, which were all white, and wrap them around themselves.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they were put into one, or two, or three boxcars coupled to the end of our train, to also be deported.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were kept in the cold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were kept in the dark.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were kept without food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were crazy to begin with.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were mentally disturbed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So at 12 o'clock at night, the gendarmes decided to open the doors and let them out into the field.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they behaved like animals.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were hungry, and they were running around screaming.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and-- and then the-- the soldier told my father, well, we used them as target practice.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What else can we do for fun?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that-- I'll never forget that, because some of these people came close to the openings.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of them actually banged, ran into the external-- to the-- to the outside of that barn from logs, and hit their heads on the-- and I could see their faces.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they looked human, but they weren't really human.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Their eyes were like the eyes of animals.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were like shining.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were-- they had a different look.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't know if it was because they were scared, or hungry, or all of it together.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's another recurrent dream that I have to this day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now we're going back to Shargorod.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] One very traumatic experience for me was the fact that there were no toilets.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
